<h1>Pet Of The Week</h1>
<br/> 
<h2>TERMS AND CONDITIONS OF ENTRY</h2>
<br/> 
Information on how to enter and prizes form part of these conditions.
<br/><br/> 
<h3>How to enter:</h3>
Entries are open each week from 12.00am Wednesday and close 11.59pm the following Tuesday. To enter email a photo of your pet to <a href="mailto:admin@petsplease.com.au">admin@petsplease.com.au</a> or enter via our Facebook page <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Petsplease">https://www.facebook.com/Petsplease</a>.
<br/><br/>
The photo submitted must be taken by the person submitting the photo, or permission has been given to the person submitting the photo, you must own copyright to the photo and give us full permission to use it on our website and on social media.
<br/><br/>
<h3>Winner evaluation process:</h3>
Your entry will be judged by a panel from Pets Please and evaluated on quality, cuteness and creativity.
 <br/><br/>
<h3>Prize includes:</h3>
Prize will be announced on a Facebook post each week. The prize is not redeemable for cash.
 <br/><br/>
<h3>Prize drawn:</h3>
The entries will be judged every Wednesday by the Pet Please panel of judges.
 <br/><br/>
The winner will be notified by Facebook, please be aware that Facebook does not allow Pets Please to PM (Private message) you, we will place a message on your photo as a reply so please respond to this message, this is a feature of Facebook, we will email any winners if provided and the winning photo will be published on the Pets Please website, social media and in the Pets Please monthly Newsletter.
 <br/><br/>
<h3>Claiming the Prize:</h3>
Claims for prizes must be made via email to admin@petsplease.com.au or through our Pets Please Facebook private message with your postal address within a month of your photo being selected as Pet Of The Week. Failure to claim a prize within this time may forfeit your prize.
<br/><br/>
Other conditions:
<ul>
	<li>The prize is non-transferable or refundable for cash.</li>
<li>Entries are open to any resident of Australia</li>    	
 <li>No employees of Pets Please or Pets Please subsidiaries are eligible for entry.</li>   	
</ul>
